6)The power cable could have been longer.

#Pros

1)The price makes it a steal offer and is very very affordable.

2)The fridge is light hence moving it around is not a issue.

3)The cooling is really fast and keeps the internal temparature steady even in long loadshedding

4)Enough space in veggie box and as well ain the fridge

5)Energy efficiency is effective barely eny difference I. my electricity bill.

6)Ice barely takes 45minits in medium settings

7)The chiller tray can hold upto 10pkts of half liter milk

8)the fridge itself is compact and does not eat up space.
